data.description: Step into luxury in this newly remodeled 2/2 corner unit with open floor plan. The kitchen is a chef's dream, boasting new cabinets, quartz countertops, island and LG stainless steel SMART appliances. Both bathrooms have been completely rejuvenated for a spa-like experience. The primary ensuite, features balcony access, walk in closet, dual sinks, and a luxurious walk in shower. Step onto not one, but two balconies-one with amazing ocean views, and the other capturing sunsets and river views. New flooring, light fixtures and ceiling fans throughout. Other features include built in wall safe, electric fireplace, laundry room w/storage and  under building parking. Updated electrical & plumbing. Popcorn ceiling was removed. Unit comes with 1 under building parking spaces. Private beach access and community pool. Coral Sands has strong HOA with reserves. Structurally sound with NO assessments. Nothing to do except enjoy the beach lifestyle!
